{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram delivery zone resolver loader (Phase 2.1a foundation).

  Loads assets/ganguram-zone-resolver.js, which defines window.GanguramZone:
    classifyPincode, getSelectedPincode, getSelectedDeliveryLocation,
    setSelectedPincode, clearSelectedDeliveryLocation.

  Foundation ONLY — defines the API and is inert on load. It does NOT render UI
  or touch cart / checkout / MOV / date-slot / product visibility / menu / search
  / banners / collection filtering. SBZ compatibility: the resolver mirrors the
  pincode to localStorage["Zipcode"].

  Render once. Currently rendered in layout/theme.liquid before </body>.

  Future override seam (no list duplication): to source the pincode lists from
  Liquid/shop metafields instead of the JS default, output a
  `window.GanguramZoneConfig = { kolkata, quickCommerce, labels }` script BEFORE
  this include. If absent, the JS default config is the single source of truth.
{%- endcomment -%}
<script src="{{ 'ganguram-zone-resolver.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
